@baseUrl = http://localhost:3001

### 공개: 아파트 목록 조회
### query keyword: name, address, description
### query filters: name, address
GET {{baseUrl}}/apartments/public?name=아파트
###
GET {{baseUrl}}/apartments/public?address=서울

