### 슈퍼관리자/관리자: 아파트 목록 조회
### query filters: name, address
### query exactFilters: apartmentStatus
### query keyword: name, address, (관계형) admin name/email
GET {{baseUrl}}/apartments?apartmentStatus=APPROVED

